verbose_text: Interestingly, levels of proteins involved in a highly mutagenic, translocation promoting, alternative NHEJ subpathway (Alt-NHEJ) were also increased in all MM cell lines, with the Alt-NHEJ protein DNA ligase IIIalpha, also overexpressed in several plasma cell samples isolated from MM patients.
evidence: Alt-NHEJ protein DNA ligase IIIalpha, also overexpressed
